//   7. Per-key rate limit: 5 failed attempts/hr -> 429 + KEY_BRUTE_FORCE security failure
//   8. If check=1 & token: validate sessionTokens entry; verify keyHash+hwid match; if IP differs
//      -> CONCURRENT_SESSION (key shared); refresh session; return "OK"
//   9. Find license by keyHash (include script.protectionProfile + hwids)
//  10. If license.scriptId !== scriptId -> INVALID_LICENSE_OR_SCRIPT_BINDING
//  11. Auto-redeem UNREDEEMED on first use (sets ACTIVE, redeemedBy=hwid, computes expiresAt)
//  12. Status checks: SUSPENDED->403, BLACKLISTED->403, EXPIRED->403 (auto-marks EXPIRED)
//  13. HWID lock: auto-bind on first use; if hwidRecord missing & existing hwids -> HWID_MISMATCH
//  14. Concurrent session: if activeSessions has keyHash with different IP+hwid -> 401
